# Git push after every phase

When a FluxFS architecture phase (1–8) is complete and tests/clippy pass:

1. Stage all relevant changes (no `target/` or secrets).
2. Commit with a conventional message, e.g. `feat(scanner): Phase 2 file scanner and index`.
3. Push to `origin main` on https://github.com/ManeeshJupalle/FluxFS.git

Do this without waiting for the user to ask, unless they explicitly say not to push.

